ve material energy. They are struck only by +1 or better magic weapons. Their psionic disciplines are clairaudience, clairvoyance, object reading, suspend animation, aura alteration, dimension walk, mind bar, and telempathic projection, all at 14th-level mastery.\n\nIn natural form an agathion appears elf-like, with luminous opalescent skin and shining eyes. A touch in that shape inflicts 7-14 points of positive power damage on an opponent. If it voluntarily leaves its chosen form, it returns to its home plane and will not come again unless called. If slain, it cannot return for 10-60 years while it regains strength.",
