d sense of smell are superior. They speak their own tongue, Ogre, common Giant, and some Common. Smarter specimens may also know humanoid languages. They are deep blue in complexion with glossy black hair, teeth, and nails, and usually greenish or yellow eyes. Their bodies are tall, thin, wiry, and muscular.",
