roups in towers worked from the natural basalt of their fiery realm. They are unfriendly, taciturn, and compassionless, but also lawful in temperament. They prize clear purple and red gems, and once an azer gives its word, that bond is considered firm.",
    "id": "monster_manual_ii_azer"
