      "npc_notes": "CAT (WILD)\n\nFREQUENCY: Uncommon\nNO. APPEARING: 1 or 2-5\nARMOR CLASS: 5\nMOVE: 18\"\nHIT DICE: 1\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 3\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-2/1-2/1-2\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Rear claws for 1-2/1-2\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: See below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Animal\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: S\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: I/10 + 1/hp\n\nWild cats are found from subarctic to tropical regions. The larger wild cat has 2 forepaw claw attacks. If both forepaw claw attacks succeed in hitting the opponent, the animal gains rear claw rakes for 1-2/1-2 points of damage.\n\nBoth sorts of felines surprise prey on 3 in 6. Both are surprised only on a 1 in 6. Both species are agile climbers and can move up and along tree limbs at half their normal movement rate.",
