ck or earth as does a xorn, taking one round to alter its molecular structure to do so. If struck by a phase door spell when altering, the creature is slain. Crysmals hate xorn, as the latter prey upon them.\n\nCrysmals appear as truncated, prismed heaps of translucent crystals. An individual tends to be of 1 color. Coloration ranges from pale amber through olive into deep violet. Medium-sized crysmals run up to 16 hit points. Large ones are 17 or more points. Those of over 28 hit point-size are about 2 feet wide, 14 feet long, and 1/2 foot thick.",
