      "npc_notes": "CRYSTAL OOZE\n\nFREQUENCY: Rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1-2\nARMOR CLASS: 8\nMOVE: 1\"//3\"\nHIT DICE: 4\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 4-16\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Paralyzing poison\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Special immunities; weapon corrosion\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: See below\nINTELLIGENCE: Animal\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: M to L\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: IV/225 + 4/hp\n\nCrystal ooze is a water-adapted variety of gray ooze. When immersed, it is 75% invisible. Any dim or dark body of shallow water may conceal one, though it can survive out of water for several hours. It attacks by flowing over a victim and exuding a paralyzing poison. The poison inflicts 4-16 points of damage and, unless the victim saves vs. poison, causes paralysis so the prey can be consumed. When prey reaches -20 hit points, it has been totally consumed.\n\nCrystal ooze is unharmed by acid, cold, heat, or fire. Electricity and magic missile affect it normally. Weapon blows inflict only 1 point per hit. Wooden weapons are vulnerable to its corrosive poison and, unless they save vs. acid for each hit, they are eaten away or broken.",
