      "level_xp_value": "1 HD = I/14 + 1/hp; 2 HD = II/28 + 2/hp; 3 HD = II/50 + 3/hp; 4 HD = III/150 + 4/hp; 5 HD = IV/205 + 5/hp; 6 HD = V/425 + 6/hp",
