      "npc_notes": "OCTON (HIERARCH MODRON)\n\nFREQUENCY: Rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1 (of 64)\nARMOR CLASS: 1\nMOVE: 9\"/9\" (MC:B)//9\"\nHIT DICE: 12+12\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 8\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-8 (x8)\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: +2 or better weapons to hit\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 30%\nINTELLIGENCE: Exceptional\nALIGNMENT: Lawful neutral\nSIZE: L (7'-0\" tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: VIII/5250 + 16/hp\n\nEach of the 64 octons governs a sector of the Plane of Nirvana. The base modrons of the sector, along with the decatons and nonatons assigned to it, are their responsibility. Octons guard their sectors most rigidly and ensure that regulations are obeyed, routine observed, and reports invariably correct.\n\nOctons move through air and water by means of a circular collar at shoulder level. This collar, which is part of the octon's body, forces air or liquid through it, giving the creature lift, propulsion, and a high degree of maneuverability. Their 8 tentacled arms are attached to the outside of this collar.\n\nOctons use spells as 14th-level clerics. They also possess the following spell-like abilities, usable once per round, at will, one at a time: water walking as the ring, haste, detection of good/evil, and telekinesis up to 3,500 gp weight. They are totally immune to psionic combat and the effects of psionics.\n\nEach octon has a personal staff consisting of 1 decaton, 1 nonaton, 5 pentadrones, 16 quadrones, 81 tridrones, 256 duodrones, and 1,728 monodrones. They maintain small towers, lesser versions of the towers of the quartons, the secundi, and Primus.",
