elementals fall into 3 hit-dice strength categories like their major-plane brethren: 16 HD by spell, 12 HD by summoning device, and 8 HD by staff. Para-elementals are impervious to attacks from weapons of less than +1 enchantment or by creatures without magical ability of 4 hit dice or less. As with ordinary elementals, control must be maintained at all times or the para-elemental will turn on its summoner. Material components are: a lens of clear crystal or glass for Ice; a damp cloth for Ooze; volcanic glass for Magma; and dry ash for Smoke.",
