      "npc_notes": "QUINTON (HIERARCH MODRON)\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1 (of 25)\nARMOR CLASS: -3\nMOVE: 6\"/6\" (MC:C)//6\"\nHIT DICE: 15+15\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 5\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 3-17 (x5)\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: +3 or better weapons to hit\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 60%\nINTELLIGENCE: Genius\nALIGNMENT: Lawful neutral\nSIZE: L\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: X/10,950 + 20/hp\n\nQuintons are the major bureau chiefs and record-keepers of Nirvana. Each has a septon and a staff of 25 pentadrones, 64 quadrones, 81 tridrones, and countless duodrones and monodrones. There are bureaus in each of the sector and quarter towers, and 5 main bureaus in the Tower of Primus at the capital, each headed by a quinton.\n\nQuintons resemble tall, stocky humanoids with 4 flexible arms jutting from the shoulders. A prehensile tail serves as the creature's fifth arm. They have fan-like wings similar to those of the hextons. As a symbol of rank, each quinton bears a diamond inscribed in its forehead indicating its post.\n\nQuintons are capable of legend lore as if the questioned object or person were at hand, taking 1-4 rounds. They may detect evil/good and detect magic at will, and may cast spells as 20th-level clerics. They are also immune to all forms of psionic attack.",
