aximum distance shown above. Thus, while it is safe to slay these monsters from a distance, they are particularly dangerous in close proximity.\n\nWounded or seriously threatened vapor rats always assume gaseous form. In that state, they can be harmed only by attack forms which destroy vapors. Such attack forms include very hot or magical fire, lightning, and exceptionally strong winds.",
