      "npc_notes": "SKUNK\n\nFREQUENCY: Common\nNO. APPEARING: 1 or 1-6\nARMOR CLASS: 8\nMOVE: 12\"\nHIT DICE: 1/4\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Squirt musk\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Squirt musk\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Animal\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: S\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: I/4 + 1/hp\n\nSkunks are found in most temperate and subtropical regions, dwelling in lightly populated and uninhabited areas. While they will bite if cornered, their major attack and defense method is to back toward threatening creatures and release a 1\" x 1\" x 1\" cloud of stinking musk. All those within must make a saving throw vs. poison. Those who succeed must retreat immediately or count as failing to save. Those who fail will be nauseated for 1-4 rounds and must retreat and retch. Each must also save again vs. poison or also be blinded for 1-4 rounds. The musk will cause normal clothing to smell so badly as to require burying or burning. Flesh, leather, metal, and so forth must be washed repeatedly for several days in order to remove the odor. Vinegar will cut the stench in only 2 or 3 washings.",
