      "npc_notes": "TERMITE, GIANT HARVESTER SOLDIER\n\nFREQUENCY: See below\nNO. APPEARING: 3-18\nARMOR CLASS: 2/8 (head/body)\nMOVE: 9\"\nHIT DICE: 2+2\n% IN LAIR: 20%\nTREASURE TYPE: See below\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-4\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Nil\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Semi-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: M (4 1/2' long)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil/nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: II/50 + 3/hp\n\nGiant harvester soldier termites share the nest and behavior of the workers. Soldier termites have strong jaws and can spit an irritating fluid similar to kerosene. This liquid blinds any creature struck unless a save vs. poison succeeds. Blindness lasts 5-20 rounds. The fluid burns if exposed to flame or heat; one quantity spit on a target and ignited inflicts 5-16 points of burning damage. The fluid can be spit only once per turn, with a range of 1\" and a volume of about 1 pint.",
