snake-like or have only one human feature, such as a head or arms. Their bite, unless from a human head, does 1-10 points of damage.\n\nAll yuan ti with human legs move 12\" per turn. Those with snake bodies move 9\" per turn and can coil around pillars and the like. Human-headed yuan ti can cast the following spells once per day: cause fear, darkness within a 15-foot radius, snake charm, stick to snakes, neutralize poison, suggestion, and polymorph other.\n\nYuan ti speak their own language. They may also speak with any snake or snake-like monster. Those with human heads also speak Chaotic and Common.",
