    },
    "npc_notes": "LOLTH (DEMON QUEEN OF SPIDERS), LESSER GODDESS\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: -10 (-2)\nMOVE: 1\"/9\"/15\"\nHIT DICE: 66 hit points (16 hit dice)\n% IN LAIR: 25%\nTREASURE TYPE: Q (x5), R\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1 and 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 4-16 + poison and (by weapon type)\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: See below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 70%\nINTELLIGENCE: Godlike\nALIGNMENT: Chaotic evil\nSIZE: L (M)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: 266\nAttack/Defense Modes: All/all\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: X/12,470*\n*for destroying Material Plane form only; if actually killed permanently, multiply X.P. by 10.\n\nLolth is a powerful demon lord who usually appears on the Prime Material Plane as a giant black widow spider, though she may also take the form of an exquisitely beautiful female dark elf; the alternate-form statistics are given in parentheses in the original entry. She can converse with all spiders, and they obey her unquestioningly. Although she has only 66 hit points, her exceptional armour class prevents most damage, and she can heal herself at will up to three times per day. In spider form she can cast 30' web strands like a web spell, except that victims also take 1-4 hit points of damage per round from poisonous exudation, and in the same round she may bite for 4-16 hit points plus death unless the victim saves against poison at -4. In humanoid form she uses drow weapons and functions as a 16th-level cleric and 14th-level magic-user, though she cannot wear armour and loses her psionic powers in that form. In spider form, at will, she may use one power per melee round from a list including comprehend languages, confusion on a creature looked at, darkness 10' radius, and dispel magic. Other powers include phase door, read magic, shape change, teleport without error, tongues, true seeing, summoning spiders, and gating in lower demons. She is unaffected by non-magical weapons, and silver harms her only if magical at +1 or better. Cold, electricity, and gas do only half damage. Acid, magic missile, and poison affect her normally. Holy water is especially harmful, doing 6 points on a splash and 6-21 points on a direct hit. Her vision extends into infrared and ultraviolet to 120', she has limited telepathy, and her psionic disciplines include body equilibrium, clairvoyance, domination, dimension walking, mind bar, molecular rearrangement, and probability travel, all at 16th-level ability.",
