    "npc_notes": "ELEMENTAL PRINCES OF EVIL, COMMON\n\nThe elemental princes of evil share several common traits. At will they may perform detect invisible, dispel magic at 20th level, infravision for one day, know alignment, suggestion lasting 12 hours, and teleport without error. They also possess a special telepathic power enabling them to understand and converse with any intelligent creature. Three times per day each may read languages and read magic, and once per day each may use telekinesis on up to 6,000 gold pieces weight. The X.P. value listed for each prince is for destroying the Material Plane form only; if a prince is killed permanently, multiply the value by 10.",
