    "npc_notes": "IMIX, PRINCE OF EVIL FIRE CREATURES\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: -4\nMOVE: 18\"\nHIT DICE: 90 hit points\n% IN LAIR: 45%\nTREASURE TYPE: R, U\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 6-36\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Fire damage; spells\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: See below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 85%\nINTELLIGENCE: Genius\nALIGNMENT: Neutral evil\nSIZE: L (18' tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: 190\nAttack/Defense Modes: All/all\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: X/25,900\n\nImix generally appears as an 18' high pillar of fire. He radiates 1-20 points of heat damage constantly to all within 10'; creatures resistant to fire take half, with no save. He attacks as a 20 hit dice creature once per round for 6-36 hit points of damage. Only +2 or better weapons can harm him. As prince of evil fire creatures, Imix may summon once per day one of the following groups: 1-3 efreet, 1-3 fire elementals, or 1-3 salamanders. Three times per day he may cause painfully bright continual light, cast a triple-strength wall of fire, and initiate pyrotechnics. Once per day he may throw a 20-dice fireball. Water attacks against Imix are at +1 hit probability, while cold attacks are at +2 hit probability and add one point of damage to each attack die. Imix is immune to paralysis, poison, and petrifaction. He lives in the depths of a monstrous active volcano on the Elemental Plane of Fire. There is great enmity between Imix and Olhydra.",
