    "npc_notes": "IRON COBRA\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: 0\nMOVE: 12\"\nHIT DICE: 1\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: See below\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1–3\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Poison\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: See below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: See below\nINTELLIGENCE: Non-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: S (3' long)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: III/88 + 1 per hit point\n\nThe iron cobra is a segmented automaton of unknown metal shaped like a snake, believed to have been created by a great magic-user or minor deity. Only a dozen or so are thought to exist, and a deactivated specimen with its control words known is valued at about 2,000 gp by high-level magic-users. It is activated and deactivated by key words set by its creator, and when active it obeys simple verbal commands. When immobile it is absolutely silent, though when moving it usually emits a soft rustling like that of a normal snake.\n\nIt has no mind, so is unaffected by spells influencing the mind, such as sleep or charm, nor by web. Non-magical weapons inflict only half damage on it. It can hide in shadows as an 8th-level thief and emits no body heat, so infravision does not detect it there. It can also strike with surprise from behind, moving in utter silence for short periods. Its bite delivers a deadly poison and 1–3 hit points of damage; the victim saves at -2. The poison supply is limited to three poisonous bites, after which the fangs inflict only 1–3 hit points. If its controller is present, the fangs can be recharged.\n\nAgainst magical spell attacks other than those already noted, the iron cobra saves as a 12th-level magic-user. It may be ordered to guard treasure, act as a bodyguard, or track down and destroy anyone whose name is known, provided that person is within one mile. In that case it homes in on psychic vibrations, which may be blocked by mind blank or a similar spell. Some iron cobras use paralysing or sleep-inducing drugs instead of poison; in that case a normal saving throw is allowed.",
