    "npc_notes": "MAGNESIUM SPIRIT\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: 0\nMOVE: 36\"\nHIT DICE: 6+1\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 3–12\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Energy and strength drain — see below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Can only be hit by silver and magical weapons; and see below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 50% and see below\nINTELLIGENCE: Very\nALIGNMENT: Lawful evil\nSIZE: M\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: VII/1,300 + 8 per hit point\n\nOnly three or four of these creatures are believed to exist. They resemble cylinders of white flame 5' tall and 3' across, with wispy tails 5' long, yet give off no noticeable heat. Their sole purpose is to inhabit the body of a human of sufficient level and use that body to perform a spell that returns them to their plane of origin. They attack only humans.\n\nThe spirit approaches at great speed, pauses within 10' of its chosen victim, and flares in a split-second flash. All observers within 20' must save versus petrification or be blinded for 12 turns, as by the blindness spell. It then attacks and always wins initiative, even against hasted foes. A hit inflicts 3–12 hit points, drains one energy level, and drains 2 points of strength, the lost strength returning at 1 point per hour while the lost level is permanent.\n\nOnce it hits, it locks onto the victim and begins merging, inflicting the same damage and drains automatically each round. After two rounds of merging, only holy water can strike it without hurting the victim; each vial inflicts 2–7 hit points and forces the spirit to abandon the attempt. If the spirit completes three rounds of merging and the victim still has at least 5 levels remaining, it uses the body to shriek out its return spell and both body and spirit vanish. If the victim has fewer than 5 levels remaining, the spirit abandons the ruined body and seeks another human host. The emptied body collapses as a mindless husk and resists resurrection except by very powerful magic such as a properly used wish. The spirit is immune to sleep, charm, hold, paralysis, and fear, and is always vulnerable to holy water.",
    "id": "fiend_folio_magnesium_spirit"
  },
