    "npc_notes": "PHANTOM STALKER\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1-2\nARMOR CLASS: 3\nMOVE: 12\"/24\"\nHIT DICE: 6\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 2\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-4/1-4\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Impervious to fire\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Semi-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: Variable — usually L\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: V/375 + 6 per hit point\n\nPhantom stalkers are servitors from the Elemental Plane of Fire, usually summoned by powerful magic-users much like invisible stalkers. They serve as bodyguards and obey orders literally, perverting the intent whenever possible. If their summoner is killed, they vanish instantly and return 1-4 hours later from the Ethereal Plane to take vengeance on the killer.\n\nThey may polymorph themselves, though they most often appear as reddish humanoids with huge fiery eyes. They attack with claws for 1-4 hit points each. Fire cannot harm them, and magical fire heals them 1 hit point per attack die. Cold attacks affect them at -2 on saves and inflict +1 damage per die. If close to death, a phantom stalker can release its life essence as a 6-dice fireball and then dematerialise.",
