    "npc_notes": "QUIPPER\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 5-50 (5% chance of 70-100)\nARMOR CLASS: 5\nMOVE: 1\"\nHIT DICE: 1-4 hit points\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-2\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Nil\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Nil\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Non-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: S (3\"-5\" long)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: I/5 + 1 per hit point\n\nQuippers are small, vicious freshwater fish. They are a rare cold-water piranha. A shoal may or may not attack swimmers or waders, but once one draws blood the whole shoal goes berserk and doubles its normal number of attacks per round.\n\nUp to 20 quippers can attack a human-sized target at once. If at least one hits on the first round, all attack the next round. If all miss, there is only a 40% chance they continue.",
