    "npc_notes": "RETRIEVER\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: -2\nMOVE: 18\"\nHIT DICE: 10\n% IN LAIR: 70%\nTREASURE TYPE: Z\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 4\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 3-18/3-18/3-18/3-18\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Eye rays\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Nil\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Low\nALIGNMENT: Chaotic evil\nSIZE: L (11' tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: VIII/4,950 + 14 per hit point\n\nRetrievers are monstrous spider-like constructs created by Demogorgon in the Abyss. Their four forelimbs end in huge cleavers, and they possess six eyes, four of which project rays. No more than two ray-eyes can function in a round, and once used each needs six rounds to recharge.\n\nThe rays are fire, cold, lightning, and transmutation. The energy rays do damage equal to the retriever’s current hit points, save versus dragon breath for half. The transmutation ray turns the victim into mud, stone, gold, or lead at random. A retriever may instead attack physically with all four cleavers, but it cannot use eye rays in the same round.",
