    "npc_notes": "SLAAD, RED\n\nFREQUENCY: Rare\nNO. APPEARING: 3-18\nARMOR CLASS: 6\nMOVE: 6\" (can hop at 9\" rate for a maximum of one turn in one hour)\nHIT DICE: 7\n% IN LAIR: 30%\nTREASURE TYPE: F\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 3\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 1-4/1-4/2-16\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: See below\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Regeneration — see below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 35%\nINTELLIGENCE: Low\nALIGNMENT: Chaotic neutral\nSIZE: L (8' tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: VI/875 + 8 per hit point\n\nThe commonest of the slaadi, the red slaad attacks with two claws and a bite. It regenerates 3 hit points per melee round while alive. Twice per day it may try to gate in 1-2 other red slaadi with a 35% chance of success. Once per day it may use power word, stun.\n\nEach successful claw hit has a 40% chance of implanting a pellet into the victim. The victim must save versus poison or die in 3-36 hours. Certain powerful spells can neutralise or remove the pellet.",
