    "npc_notes": "SSENDAM\n\nFREQUENCY: Very rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: -6\nMOVE: 15\"/18\"\nHIT DICE: 197 hit points\n% IN LAIR: 30%\nTREASURE TYPE: A (x4), F (x2)\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 3 or 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: 2-16/2-16/2-16 plus drain levels or special\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Spells\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Regeneration, spells; +3 or better weapon to hit\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: 85%\nINTELLIGENCE: Supra genius\nALIGNMENT: Chaotic neutral\nSIZE: M\nPSIONIC ABILITY: 379\nAttack/Defense Modes: All/all\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: X/28,695*\n*for destroying material form only — if actually killed permanently, multiply by 10\n\nSsendam is a slaad lord who either appears as a man bearing the Black Sword or as a golden amoeba with a man’s brain for a nucleus. In amoebic form he attacks with three pseudopods, each doing 2-16 damage and draining 1-4 experience levels.\n\nAt will he may use fear, darkness, blink, ESP, know alignment, dispel magic at 32nd level, detect invisibility, detect magic, locate object, flame strike at double power, ultravision, mass charm, astral projection, symbol of insanity, death spell, and advanced illusion. He may gate in any slaad except Ygorl automatically and at will.",
