    "npc_notes": "SNYAD, PESTIE\n\nFREQUENCY: Uncommon\nNO. APPEARING: 1-8\nARMOR CLASS: -4\nMOVE: 21\"\nHIT DICE: 1-1\n% IN LAIR: 95%\nTREASURE TYPE: J\nNO. OF ATTACKS: Nil\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: Nil\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Nil\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: See below\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Low\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: S (2½' tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: I/7 + 1 per hit point\n\nSnyads are small light-brown bipeds with very high dexterity. They live in tiny side-passages adjoining dungeon corridors. They are silent and very fast, achieving surprise 90% of the time. They do not attack; their sole object is to steal small treasure items such as gems, coins, jewelry, and small weapons.",
