    "npc_notes": "YELLOW MUSK CREEPER\n\nFREQUENCY: Rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1\nARMOR CLASS: 7\nMOVE: Immobile\nHIT DICE: 3\n% IN LAIR: 100%\nTREASURE TYPE: Any\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 2-12\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: Special\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Nil\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Nil\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Non-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral\nSIZE: L\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: III/65 + 3 per hit point\n\nThe yellow musk creeper is a large climbing plant with bright yellow flowers. When approached within 10 feet, its flowers sway hypnotically. A successful hit means a flower puffs musk-laden dust into the victim’s face; the victim must save versus magic or walk entranced into the plant.\n\nOnce inside, aerial roots attach to the skull and devour the victim’s brain at 1-4 intelligence points per round. If intelligence drops to 0 or below, the victim dies; if reduced to 1 or 2, the victim becomes a yellow musk zombie. The only way to kill the creeper is to destroy its buried bulbous root.",
    "id": "fiend_folio_yellow_musk_creeper"
  },
