    "npc_notes": "ZOMBIE, YELLOW MUSK\n\nFREQUENCY: Rare\nNO. APPEARING: 1-2\nARMOR CLASS: Variable\nMOVE: As human\nHIT DICE: 2\n% IN LAIR: Nil\nTREASURE TYPE: Nil\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: By weapon type\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Nil\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: Nil\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: See below\nINTELLIGENCE: Non-\nALIGNMENT: Neutral evil\nSIZE: M\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\nLEVEL/X.P. VALUE: II/28 + 2 per hit point\n\nYellow musk zombies are victims of the creeper whose intelligence has been reduced to 1 or 2. They become mindless, yellow-skinned servants under the plant’s control, attempting to lure or drag new victims to it. They keep the same hit points, armour, weapons, and possessions they had before capture, but attack as 2 HD monsters and lose access to spells, psionics, and dexterity or wisdom bonuses.\n\nThey serve the parent plant for two months, then wander off and die, whereupon the implanted seed sprouts into a new yellow musk creeper. They are not true undead and cannot be turned, but they are immune to mind-affecting spells.",
