    "npc_notes": "KOBOLD, BODYGUARD\n\nFREQUENCY: Uncommon\nNO. APPEARING: 1 in lair\nARMOR CLASS: [not separately given]\nMOVE: 6\"\nHIT DICE: [not separately given]\n% IN LAIR: 40%\nTREASURE TYPE: Individuals J, O; Q (×5) in lair\nNO. OF ATTACKS: 1\nDAMAGE/ATTACK: [best available weapon]\nSPECIAL ATTACKS: Nil\nSPECIAL DEFENSES: -1 to hit in bright sunlight\nMAGIC RESISTANCE: Standard\nINTELLIGENCE: Average (low)\nALIGNMENT: Lawful evil\nSIZE: S (3' tall)\nPSIONIC ABILITY: Nil\nAttack/Defense Modes: Nil\n\nNotes: A kobold lair always contains the chief and his bodyguard, but the visible text does not provide a separate full combat line for the bodyguard beyond that statement. Chief and guard types always have the best available weapons. Otherwise, the bodyguard follows the normal kobold traits unless a fuller stat line appears elsewhere in the source.",
